[SN]TITLE[SN]
Father-of-four dies after Cardigan car and bike crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A father-of-four has died after a crash involving a car and a motorcycle.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Karl Kraus, 37, died following the crash which happened at about 12:00 BST on Sunday on the A487 at Penparc, Cardigan.
He leaves his wife Suzi Kraus, sons Ollie and Liam and step children Chloe and Kai.
Dyfed-Powys Police said the crash involved a black Yamaha motorcycle and a silver VW Golf and appealed for any witnesses to come forward.
